sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as Application
    participant ShareExt as Share Extension
    participant System as System

    User->>App: Initiate share action
    App->>ShareExt: Request sharing options
    ShareExt->>User: Display sharing options
    User->>ShareExt: Select sharing option
    ShareExt->>System: Send shared content
    System->>ShareExt: Confirm receipt
    ShareExt->>App: Notify sharing success
    App->>User: Display success message